                <h1>What is a Transparent Image? Understand PNGs</h1>
                <p>A picture with no background is commonly referred to as a "transparent image" or "PNG image." This type of image allows the subject to stand out without any distracting backgrounds, making it perfect for graphic design, presentations, or web use. Transparent images create seamless integration for logos and other visual elements.</p>
